 <span class=\"green-keyword\">variable</span> called <span class=\"green-keyword\">year</span> with an appropriate comment.</span>","keywords":["variable","year"],"correctCode":"year\\s*=\\s*\\d+","useRegex":true},{"html":"<span style=\"font-size:0.9rem\">Create a <span class=\"green-keyword\">variable</span> called <span class=\"green-keyword\">superpower</span> with an appropriate comment.</span>","keywords":["variable","superpower"],"correctCode":"superpower\\s*=\\s*(?:\"[^\"]*\"|'[^']*')","useRegex":true}];
